app: 锐捷上网行为管理系统
seo: 锐捷,上网行为管理,naborTable RCE,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测锐捷上网行为管理系统的naborTable远程代码执行漏洞，通过构造特定请求验证是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the naborTable Remote Code Execution vulnerability in Ruijie Network Behavior Management System by constructing specific requests to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
